articles.title: Wanted Islamic State commander killed by U.S., Iraqi forces, officials say - CBS News
articles.description: Iraqi forces and American troops last month killed a senior commander with the Islamic State group, as well as several other prominent militants, U.S. Central Command and Iraq's military said on Friday.
